700107f-a.title: Bronx: 144th Street (East) - Wales Avenue
700107f-a.text:
E. 144th Street, at the N. W. corner of Wales Avenue, view-
ing east across the latter and showing a very old frame house and
barn, in a neighborhood which has, since the olden days, changed
into an industrial area.
August 16, 1940
P. L. Sperr
NO REPRODUCTIONS

702003f-a.title: Bronx: Wales Avenue - 144th Street (East)
702003f-a.text:
429 Wales Ave., west side, between East 144th and East 145th
Streets.
About 1923.
W. B. Vernam.
MAY BE REPRODUCED.
